Name: io_lib
Version: 1.11.6
Epoch: 0
Release: %{revision}.%{distro}
Source0: %{name}-%{version}.1.tar.gz
License: BSD
Group: Applications/Bioinformatics
Packager: Allen Day <allenday@ucla.edu>
